description: Single story block home in a perfect Tempe location.  At the end of the cul-de-sac means large expanded lot with with plenty of room for toys, RV, and storage.  No HOA!! Very quiet yet in the middle of everything.  A quick drive or bike to ASU or 10 minutes to the airport/Scottsdale/spring training etc.  Newly painted interior with expanded living room for that open floor plan concept.  South facing patio means great shade and year round enjoyment of the huge grass yard.  Multiple storage options including a detached room that was used as an office but could also be an exercise room, complete with flooring and AC!  Easy to show!
